.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "May 2026" "Simple Shell" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
simple_shell - a simple UNIX command line interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
./hsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
simple_shell is a basic shell written in C.
It reads commands from standard input and executes them using execve.
.SH COMPILATION
gcc -Wall -Werror -Wextra -pedantic -std=gnu89 *.c -o hsh
